{
  "stem": "12289.2",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then-- then when Raoul Wallenberg comes, then-- then he, with his ingenuity and inventiveness and all that, he-- when he saw these-- these certificates I had issued, he said, well, this is fine.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But perhaps we could make them more spectacular.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that is how this Schutz-Pass, protective passports came about in Swedish colors and the Swedish coat of arms on and all that and so on.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then how he negotiated then with the then Hungarian government and got the approval of 4,500 passports.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the-- the holders of this passport could then be hidden or lodged in houses, Swedish houses or so-called Swedish houses, which we rented or bought, with the help of American money.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Because there, it was the American initiative, all this mission.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the Americans were financing Raoul Wallenberg's action behind the scene.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Pardon?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well-- well, of course, I had met him long before.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I met him in Sweden.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we were students together.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I met him when he came to Budapest as a businessman.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He was working in a business firm in Stockholm, so he came there in '42, '43, already, long before all this happened.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I knew him very well.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So when I now met him for this mission, I-- I knew that he was-- was the right man for the job.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Did you know the purpose of his mission, when he came?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, certainly.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We asked-- we asked for-- for-- for some more staff.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the-- the first idea was to send Count Bernadotte, Folke Bernadotte, with the Red Cross delegation to Budapest.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But Bernadotte never got the visa, the permission, by the Hungarians or the Germans, to-- to-- to go there.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So then, it so happened that Raoul Wallenberg volunteered.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he was and sent-- sent there.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
